_sText:
In this map you are in a hedgemaze and it's pretty large. There are 8 secrets and one of them leads to a snowland. There are many cades to build in the maze and there are three houses that you can cade in. In the graveyard there is a secret that opens a passage to underground. There is a VIP area but you will have to find that out yourself!

Want to go to a pro zombiemod server with friendly admins, many different skins to choose from and much more? Go to 66.150.214.34:27015 for all of these things!
